## Mandatory Task / Repository Match Gate
Before writing any file, confirm the current TASK explicitly includes
`livemask-app` as primary/affected repository or this App window is named in the
Cursor handoff. If it does not match, stop and report:

```text
BLOCKED: current repository does not match TASK scope.
Current repo: livemask-app
Task: <TASK-ID>
Expected repos: <list from TASK>
No files changed.
```

